{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838967814,"sessionID":"ses_287c18a69ffeFMK17cNG6zQCjE","part":{"id":"prt_d784037df001XlRP8h6Ak2PzhE","messageID":"msg_d783efb80001lc2hzOv01NHQyv","sessionID":"ses_287c18a69ffeFMK17cNG6zQCjE","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-895e045088ad45a89cda1ec4ca39db96","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md","content":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n---\n\n## GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios\n\n### Requirement: Package structure and registration\n\nThe system SHALL define the `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` with proper package structure, scheme registration, and CRD markers for controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: Package structure exists\n- **GIVEN** the repository root at `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **WHEN** examining `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **THEN** the directory SHALL contain:\n  - `doc.go` with `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` marker\n  - `register.go` with `SchemeGroupVersion` set to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n  - `agentruntime_types.go` with `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types\n  - `codeinterpreter_types.go` with `CodeInterpreter` and `CodeInterpreterList` types\n  - `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (generated)\n\n#### Scenario: Scheme group version is correct\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** `SchemeGroupVersion` SHALL be `schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n\n#### Scenario: Group version kind registration\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n- **WHEN** the `addKnownTypes` function is invoked\n- **THEN** it SHALL register `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, and `CodeInterpreterList` with the scheme\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntime type definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `AgentRuntime` as a Kubernetes-style typed object with `TypeMeta`, `ObjectMeta`, `Spec`, and `Status`.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime struct shape\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntime` struct definition\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta` and have `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec` and `Status AgentRuntimeStatus` fields with JSON tags `spec` and `status`\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntimeList struct shape\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeList` struct definition\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta`, have `metav1.ListMeta` with JSON tag `metadata`, and `Items []AgentRuntime` with JSON tag `items`\n\n#### Scenario: CRD markers on AgentRuntime\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining type-level markers\n- **THEN** the `AgentRuntime` type SHALL have:\n  - `+genclient` marker\n  - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n  - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntimeSpec definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeSpec` with required fields for session management and pod templating.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntimeSpec fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain fields:\n  - `MaxSessionDuration string` with JSON tag `maxSessionDuration`\n  - `SessionTimeout string` with JSON tag `sessionTimeout`\n  - `TargetPort []TargetPort` with JSON tag `targetPort`\n  - `PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec` with JSON tag `podTemplate`\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntimeSpec required fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct markers\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` or equivalent kubebuilder markers for `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, and `podTemplate` fields\n\n#### Scenario: MaxSessionDuration default\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `MaxSessionDuration` field marker\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` marker\n\n#### Scenario: SessionTimeout default\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `SessionTimeout` field marker\n- **THEN** it SHALL have `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: TargetPort type definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `TargetPort` to specify how traffic is routed to the agent runtime pod.\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort struct fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `TargetPort` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain:\n  - `Port int32` with JSON tag `port` (required)\n  - `Protocol ProtocolType` with JSON tag `protocol` (enum: HTTP, HTTPS)\n  - `Name string` with JSON tag `name` (optional)\n  - `PathPrefix string` with JSON tag `pathPrefix` (optional)\n\n#### Scenario: ProtocolType enum definition\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `ProtocolType` type definition\n- **THEN** it SHALL be a string type with `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` marker and constants `ProtocolHTTP` and `ProtocolHTTPS`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntimeStatus definition\n\nThe system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeStatus` with standard Kubernetes condition fields.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntimeStatus fields\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct\n- **THEN** the struct SHALL contain `Conditions []metav1.Condition` with JSON tag `conditions`\n\n#### Scenario: Conditions field markers\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** examining the `Conditions` field\n- **THEN** it SHALL have:\n  - `+kubebuilder:validation:Optional` marker\n  - `+listType=map` marker\n  - `+listMapKey=type` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: DeepCopy generation\n\nThe system SHALL generate `DeepCopy` methods for all types using controller-gen.\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntime\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (after `make generate`)\n- **WHEN** examining generated code\n- **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntime) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntime)` SHALL exist and correctly copy all nested fields including `Spec.TargetPort` slice\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeList\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- **WHEN** examining generated code\n- **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeList) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeList)` SHALL exist and correctly copy `Items` slice\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeSpec\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- **WHEN** examining generated code\n- **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeSpec) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeSpec)` SHALL exist\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for TargetPort\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- **WHEN** examining generated code\n- **THEN** `func (in *TargetPort) DeepCopyInto(out *TargetPort)` SHALL exist\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopyInto for AgentRuntimeStatus\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- **WHEN** examining generated code\n- **THEN** `func (in *AgentRuntimeStatus) DeepCopyInto(out *AgentRuntimeStatus)` SHALL exist\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: CRD generation\n\nThe system SHALL generate CRD YAML that matches the expected schema from `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`.\n\n#### Scenario: CRD generation command\n- **GIVEN** the repository with types defined in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-crd`\n- **THEN** the command SHALL invoke `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated CRD metadata\n- **GIVEN** the generated `manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`\n- **WHEN** examining the CRD\n- **THEN** `metadata.name` SHALL be `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- AND `spec.group` SHALL be `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- AND `spec.names.kind` SHALL be `AgentRuntime`\n- AND `spec.names.plural` SHALL be `agentruntimes`\n- AND `spec.scope` SHALL be `Namespaced`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated CRD version\n- **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n- **WHEN** examining `spec.versions`\n- **THEN** there SHALL be exactly one version with `name: v1alpha1`, `served: true`, and `storage: true`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated CRD spec schema\n- **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n- **WHEN** examining `spec.versions[0].schema.openAPIV3Schema.properties.spec`\n- **THEN** the `required` array SHALL include `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, and `podTemplate`\n- AND `properties.maxSessionDuration.default` SHALL be `\"8h\"`\n- AND `properties.sessionTimeout.default` SHALL be `\"15m\"`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated CRD status subresource\n- **GIVEN** the generated CRD\n- **WHEN** examining `spec.versions[0]`\n- **THEN** `subresources.status` SHALL be present\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Client-go code generation compatibility\n\nThe system SHALL define types compatible with `k8s.io/code-generator` for generating typed clients, informers, and listers.\n\n#### Scenario: Group version registration for client-gen\n- **GIVEN** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go`\n- **WHEN** reading the file\n- **THEN** `SchemeBuilder` SHALL be defined using `NewSchemeBuilder` and `AddToScheme` SHALL be exposed as `localSchemeBuilder.AddToScheme(scheme)`\n\n#### Scenario: Types implement runtime.Object\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types\n- **WHEN** the DeepCopy methods are generated\n- **THEN** both types SHALL implement `runtime.Object` interface via `DeepCopyObject()` method\n\n#### Scenario: Client generation command\n- **GIVEN** types in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- **WHEN** running `make gen-client`\n- **THEN** `hack/update-codegen.sh` SHALL be invoked, which runs `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with:\n  - `--with-watch` flag\n  - `--output-dir client-go`\n  - `--output-pkg github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n  - Input API at `runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated typed client exists\n- **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n- **WHEN** examining `client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeInterface` SHALL define methods: `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `DeleteCollection`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated informer exists\n- **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n- **WHEN** examining `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeInformer` interface SHALL define `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister`\n\n#### Scenario: Generated lister exists\n- **GIVEN** client-go code generation completed\n- **WHEN** examining `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntimeLister` interface SHALL define `List(selector labels.Selector)` and `AgentRuntimes(namespace string)` methods"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/deployment/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775838967802,"end":1775838967812}}}}
